  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..22
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    PREFIX_BLOCK@6..14
      WORD_KEY@6..7
        WORD@6..7 "b"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      OPEN_BRACE@8..9 "{"
      NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
      SPACE@10..12 "  "
      CLOSE_BRACE@12..13 "}"
      NEWLINE@13..14 "\n"
    SPACE@14..16 "  "
    ENTRY@16..20
      WORD_KEY@16..17
        WORD@16..17 "c"
      SPACE@17..18 " "
      INTEGER@18..19
        NUMERAL@18..19 "1"
      NEWLINE@19..20 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@20..21 "}"
    NEWLINE@21..22 "\n"
```

